All of you can stay in the last compound.

45
00:04:32,400 --> 00:04:35,000
All the students can stay in the surrounding compound.

46
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,200
In the evening, Master will personally appear

47
00:04:37,200 --> 00:04:39,400
to welcome everyone.

48
00:04:39,400 --> 00:04:42,200
All of you stay inside the inn.
If you need anything,

49
00:04:42,200 --> 00:04:44,600
please inform us.

50
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:46,300
It’s not necessary to stay.

51
00:04:46,300 --> 00:04:48,600
Just thank the Elder of Nalan clan on our behalf.

52
00:04:48,600 --> 00:04:51,200
We still have things we must do.

53
00:04:51,200 --> 00:04:54,600
Ice Emperor Hai Bodong welcomes Young Master Xiao.

54
