Let's go and see.

55
00:05:02,200 --> 00:05:06,000
Ice Emperor Hai Bodong welcomes Young Master Xiao

56
00:05:06,000 --> 00:05:08,000
with gifts and seeks an audience.

57
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,300
(Silver Dragon Inn)

58
00:05:15,700 --> 00:05:18,000
May I ask who is the Young Master of the Xiao family?

59
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,400
Oh, Xiao Yan...

60
00:05:19,400 --> 00:05:21,200
We know Young Master is at Yin City.

61
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:23,800
Lord Hai asked us brothers to deliver an invitation

62
00:05:23,800 --> 00:05:26,000
and prepared more than a dozen trunks of supplements.

63
00:05:26,000 --> 00:05:28,200
They’re all some food and clothing for daily use.

64
00:05:28,200 --> 00:05:30,600
Young Master is staying in Yin City and
when you have free time,

65
00:05:30,600 --> 00:05:33,400
Lord Hai will come to visit in person.

66
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:36,600
Everyone within Yin City

67
00:05:36,600 --> 00:05:38,600
listens to the Lord.

68
00:05:38,600 --> 00:05:41,500
Young Master. Please.

69
00:05:52,400 --> 00:05:54,300
Sirs, I’m not Xiao Yan.

70
00:05:54,300 --> 00:05:56,800
When Xiao Yan entered the citadel, he left right away earlier.

71
00:05:56,800 --> 00:06:00,800
Before he left, he said he was going to
find Ice Emperor Hai Bodong.

72
00:06:00,800 --> 00:06:04,600
Are you the Lang Ya Brothers?

73
00:06:04,600 --> 00:06:07,500
Elder is overpraising.
It’s not worth mentioning.

74
00:06:08,600 --> 00:06:10,800
Elder’s gifts can’t be declined.

75
00:06:10,800 --> 00:06:13,000
I wonder if both Sirs can trust me.

76
00:06:13,000 --> 00:06:15,400
I will accept these items first for Xiao Yan.

77
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:18,400
You came all the way here and cannot
reply to Lord Hai if we don't accept them.

78
00:06:18,400 --> 00:06:20,400
That’s very good. We’re troubling you

79
00:06:20,400 --> 00:06:23,500
to give them to Young Master Xiao Yan.

80
00:06:25,640 --> 00:06:28,000
- We're taking our leave.
- I won't walk you out.

81
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:34,400
His father-in-law is so wealthy.
Xiao Yan actually doesn’t want it?

82
00:06:34,400 --> 00:06:36,000
I must ask the Little Medicine Fairy later

83
00:06:36,000 --> 00:06:39,000
- if she has a younger sister.
- Very expensive.

84
00:06:39,000 --> 00:06:41,000
He impulsively said it and said it wasn’t serious.

85
00:06:41,000 --> 00:06:43,900
But Little Medicine Fairy took it seriously.

86
00:06:44,800 --> 00:06:48,000
Junior Sister, isn’t Xiao Yan looking for Hai Bodong

87
00:06:48,000 --> 00:06:51,300
to personally explain this matter? Right?

88
00:06:51,300 --> 00:06:54,600
Elder Tengshan. I'm requesting a vacation
on behalf of my Young Lady.

89
00:06:54,600 --> 00:06:57,000
Old Master misses Young Lady.

90
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:59,400
I’ll take her back to see him.

91
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:01,400
Yanran, go back home and stay

92
00:07:01,400 --> 00:07:03,900
to let Old Master be happy.

93
00:07:07,000 --> 00:07:08,500
Go.

94
00:07:15,600 --> 00:07:17,000
Young Lady.

95
00:07:19,560 --> 00:07:20,980
What's going on?

96
00:07:24,900 --> 00:07:27,100
Go back and you will know.

97
00:08:00,400 --> 00:08:02,600
Husband!

98
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:10,400
Little Medicine Fairy.
Did you hit me a moment ago?

99
00:08:12,100 --> 00:08:16,600
I followed you all the way.
You didn’t know it was me.

100
00:08:16,600 --> 00:08:19,800
No. I really didn’t know.

101
00:08:19,800 --> 00:08:20,800
Really didn’t know.

102
00:08:20,800 --> 00:08:23,800
This is my husband.
Call him Big Brother.

103
00:08:23,800 --> 00:08:26,000
Big Brother.

104
00:08:26,000 --> 00:08:28,200
Quickly go tell others
when they see Big Brother on the street,

105
00:08:28,200 --> 00:08:29,600
they must greet him. Did you hear me?

106
00:08:29,600 --> 00:08:30,800
Yes.

107
00:08:30,800 --> 00:08:32,000
Hurry. Go!

108
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,900
No. That's not necessary.

109
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,600
Xiao Yan is Big Brother!

110
00:08:37,600 --> 00:08:39,100
Big Brother!

111
00:08:40,600 --> 00:08:43,300
Husband. Let’s go home and eat.

112
00:08:46,900 --> 00:08:48,299
Father!

113
00:08:48,299 --> 00:08:50,999
Son-in-law. You came.

114
00:08:51,000 --> 00:08:53,600
I missed you. Come. Let's go inside. Please.

115
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,900
Go.

116
00:08:59,700 --> 00:09:02,100
Daughter, where's the wine?

117
00:09:03,700 --> 00:09:06,200
Do you regard me as a servant?

118
00:09:07,500 --> 00:09:10,400
Though son-in-law came,
you don't need to be so outspoken.

119
00:09:10,400 --> 00:09:12,500
You dare to bully your dad. Really.

120
00:09:12,500 --> 00:09:15,400
- Who's bullying?
- Senior, please forgive me.

121
00:09:17,000 --> 00:09:18,400
What is happening?

122
00:09:18,400 --> 00:09:21,400
I already told to you last time that

123
00:09:21,400 --> 00:09:22,800
at Magical Beast Mountain Range,

124
00:09:22,800 --> 00:09:26,400
Little Medicine Fairy was discouraged.
She wholeheartedly wanted to die.

125
00:09:26,400 --> 00:09:30,000
In a moment of desperation,
I said I wanted to marry her.

126
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,200
So this matter can't be taken seriously.

127
00:09:32,200 --> 00:09:35,700
Senior, please take back the words "son-in-law".

128
00:09:35,700 --> 00:09:40,700
Furthermore, Little Medicine Fairy, please forgive me.

129
00:09:42,600 --> 00:09:46,000
What? Do you dislike both of us?

130
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,400
I don't dare.

131
00:09:47,400 --> 00:09:51,200
It's if I don't speak the truth,
I'll feel ashamed in my heart.

132
00:09:56,000 --> 00:09:58,600
It's all your fault then.

133
00:09:58,600 --> 00:10:01,200
I knew you would come to Yin City.
I prepared for half a month.

134
00:10:01,200 --> 00:10:03,200
I especially invited two great 9-star fighters,

135
00:10:03,200 --> 00:10:05,400
the Lang Ya Brothers to let you be in the limelight.

136
00:10:05,400 --> 00:10:08,500
People outside still call me Lord Hai,

137
00:10:08,500 --> 00:10:11,200
how come I don't worth anything to you?

138
00:10:11,200 --> 00:10:12,200
I don't dare. I don't dare.

139
00:10:12,200 --> 00:10:13,600
You already dared.

140
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,200
This is the truth.

141
00:10:15,200 --> 00:10:18,200
If I don't say anything,
it would be disrespecting Senior.

142
00:10:18,200 --> 00:10:20,800
Don't call me Senior! I'm still very young.

143
00:10:20,800 --> 00:10:23,200
Daughter, what do you say about this?

144
00:10:23,200 --> 00:10:25,500
What is there to say?

145
00:10:27,000 --> 00:10:29,900
Both of us were foolishly happy.

146
00:10:29,900 --> 00:10:32,200
Husband never liked me.

147
00:10:32,200 --> 00:10:33,800
It was all lies.

148
00:10:33,800 --> 00:10:35,400
It's not like that. I...

149
00:10:35,400 --> 00:10:37,400
Then how is it?

150
00:10:38,200 --> 00:10:42,400
Since childhood, I and the Nalan family
had a marriage contract.

151
00:10:42,400 --> 00:10:45,800
Oh, it turns out you're still counting on
being an ideal son-in-law of the Nalan family.

152
00:10:45,800 --> 00:10:48,600
Daughter, he is apparently too good for us.

153
00:10:48,600 --> 00:10:51,800
Senior, it was in the past.

154
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:54,000
It's no longer valid.

155
00:10:54,900 --> 00:10:57,800
When the Nalan family broke the marriage contract,

156
00:10:57,800 --> 00:11:02,000
not only did it humiliate me
but also my father and the Xiao family.

157
00:11:02,000 --> 00:11:05,000
So I and the Nalan family set a three-year apppointment

158
00:11:05,000 --> 00:11:08,200
to take revenge and wipe out the grudge.
This major event is unfinished.

159
00:11:08,200 --> 00:11:11,200
How can I dare to discuss marriage?

160
00:11:11,200 --> 00:11:12,600
Besides, father doesn't know yet.

161
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:15,200
The relatives also haven't heard the news.
I'm still attending school.

162
00:11:15,200 --> 00:11:18,800
So how can I agree to this?

163
00:11:18,800 --> 00:11:20,400
I came today

164
00:11:20,400 --> 00:11:23,800
to face death and receive your punishment.

165
00:11:23,800 --> 00:11:25,400
I don't want to hear you say those useless things.

166
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:29,000
I only want to ask you one thing.
Do you like my daughter?

167
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:32,000
Father, can you not humiliate me?

168
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:34,000
This matter isn't....

169
00:11:37,600 --> 00:11:41,800
Like or not. It's a matter between the two of us.

170
00:11:41,800 --> 00:11:44,400
Little Medicine Fairy understands me.
I also understand her.

171
00:11:44,400 --> 00:11:46,200
After I settle the appointment with Nalan Clan,

172
00:11:46,200 --> 00:11:49,800
fate will tell us where we are going
and what the future holds.

173
00:11:49,800 --> 00:11:53,600
But a noble man should do things clearly
and should not mess it around.

174
00:11:53,600 --> 00:11:57,200
Saying it like that means you like my daughter.

175
00:11:57,200 --> 00:12:00,000
Since that's the case, it's proper to discuss it.

176
00:12:00,000 --> 00:12:01,400
Sit.

177
00:12:07,900 --> 00:12:09,500
Well,

178
00:12:09,500 --> 00:12:13,000
how about I get rid of that old Nalan Jie?

179
00:12:13,000 --> 00:12:16,000
Don't joke around. How is that possible?

180
00:12:17,000 --> 00:12:19,000
Don't just see the messiness of my store.

181
00:12:19,000 --> 00:12:21,800
This is the wealthiest place in Chu Yun Empire.

182
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:24,100
I have so much 6-grade and 7-grade medicine
that I literally can stomp on them.

183
00:12:24,100 --> 00:12:27,400
And I have thousands of 6-grade
and 7-grade Magical Crystals.

184
00:12:27,400 --> 00:12:31,500
Even the collections in the royal palace
are less than what I have here.

185
00:12:32,600 --> 00:12:35,200
In terms of Fight Techniques,

186
00:12:35,200 --> 00:12:38,000
I have what the Five Great Clans have
and I also have what they don't have.

187
00:12:38,000 --> 00:12:41,200
I don't even collect the Fight Techniques
that are below Earth Rank.

188
00:12:41,200 --> 00:12:44,800
Just nod kid, then they can all be yours.

189
00:12:44,800 --> 00:12:46,800
I also have a map

190
00:12:46,800 --> 00:12:49,000
to the Snake People Empire.

191
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:52,600
Over there, you can find Green Lotus Earth Core Flame
(Born in the deepest parts of the earth).

192
00:12:52,600 --> 00:12:55,400
One of the twenty-three kind of Essence Flame.

193
00:12:55,400 --> 00:12:57,400
If you can find it, it can also be yours.

194
00:12:57,400 --> 00:13:00,000
Just say the word.

195
00:13:00,800 --> 00:13:03,500
-Green Lotus Earth Core Flame?
-Yup.

196
00:13:06,600 --> 00:13:11,400
My lord, I can't do it.

197
00:13:12,700 --> 00:13:14,000
"Can't do it".

198
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,800
Get up!

199
00:13:15,800 --> 00:13:18,200
I, Hai Bodong, never pretend to be nice and kind.

200
00:13:18,200 --> 00:13:21,400
Say one more word, and I will hit you to death.

201
00:13:21,400 --> 00:13:23,200
Let's me ask you one more time:

202
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:27,000
yes or no?

203
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,800
No!

204
00:13:39,800 --> 00:13:42,000
You were scared, weren't you?

205
00:13:43,000 --> 00:13:44,200
Scared!

206
00:13:44,200 --> 00:13:46,800
Look at him! He was so scared!

207
00:13:46,800 --> 00:13:49,500
Let me see if he peed himself.

208
00:13:56,600 --> 00:13:57,600
Look at him.

209
00:13:57,600 --> 00:14:00,100
My dad was messing with you!

210
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:06,600
-Come sit, Husband.
-I wrote to your father once I came back.

211
00:14:06,600 --> 00:14:09,400
Your father said that he can't decide for you.

212
00:14:09,400 --> 00:14:12,300
He said you will always accomplish what you decided to do.

213
00:14:12,300 --> 00:14:14,800
My son-in-law, you have to thank me.

214
00:14:14,800 --> 00:14:17,300
I spent lots of energy

215
00:14:17,300 --> 00:14:20,800
talking my daughter out of going after you.

216
00:14:38,850 --> 00:14:40,640
I didn't get to eat anything.

217
00:14:42,700 --> 00:14:45,900
Xiao Yan? I was just waiting for you.
Let's go eat grilled meat.

218
00:14:45,900 --> 00:14:48,260
I've already eaten and drunk to my full.
You guys go ahead.

219
00:14:48,260 --> 00:14:51,410
Hey, your father-in-law sure treats you well.

220
00:14:51,410 --> 00:14:54,600
Stop it. How does the house of Nalan treat you bad?

221
00:14:55,620 --> 00:14:59,380
Don't even mention it.
When we went in, the food was already set out.

222
00:14:59,380 --> 00:15:03,760
But they said Nalan Jie was vomiting blood,
so we had to come back. Isn't it annoying?

223
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:05,730
Nalan Jie vomited blood?

224
00:15:07,210 --> 00:15:09,200
Student Xiao Yan,

225
00:15:09,200 --> 00:15:10,990
come to my room.

226
00:15:10,990 --> 00:15:12,460
Yes.

227
00:15:47,700 --> 00:15:48,920
What are you doing?

228
00:15:48,920 --> 00:15:51,560
I beg you, please save my grandfather.

229
00:15:51,560 --> 00:15:54,610
If you don't want to,
I'm willing to stake my life for

230
00:15:54,610 --> 00:15:57,610
the damage that Uncle Xiao
and the Xiao Family have received.

231
00:16:10,800 --> 00:16:12,410
Don't say that.

232
00:16:12,970 --> 00:16:15,420
Come. Get up first.

233
00:16:15,420 --> 00:16:17,870
- Elder Tengshan.
- Get up.

234
00:16:23,160 --> 00:16:26,550
Go wait outside the door.
I will talk with Xiao Yan.

235
00:16:30,990 --> 00:16:32,330
Yes.

236
00:16:52,410 --> 00:16:56,520
Elder Tengshan, please clarify.

237
00:16:57,170 --> 00:17:00,430
Nalan Jie fell under the Lao Poison.

238
00:17:01,450 --> 00:17:04,030
How much do you know about the Blood Sect?

239
00:17:04,030 --> 00:17:07,480
Not much. What do you ask?

240
00:17:07,480 --> 00:17:11,740
It's about life and death.
Even though you hate me, you have to tell me the truth.

241
00:17:11,740 --> 00:17:15,960
The most terrifying thing about the Blood Sect
is that they have poisonous insects.

242
00:17:15,960 --> 00:17:18,020
Which is Gu.

243
00:17:18,020 --> 00:17:22,020
Once you get poisoned by them,
Gu will get into your blood stream,

244
00:17:22,020 --> 00:17:25,810
and you will do whatever they tell you to do.

245
00:17:27,190 --> 00:17:29,230
No wonder.

246
00:17:29,230 --> 00:17:32,400
- You knew?
- No wonder she said at the Magical Beast Mountain Range

247
00:17:32,400 --> 00:17:34,530
that it's related to
the life and death of our two families.

248
00:17:35,130 --> 00:17:38,650
But it was the life and death of only her clan.

249
00:17:42,070 --> 00:17:44,230
Your prejudice is too deep.

